These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, disco, ambient, punk
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of ambient and the fan of punk##2
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | punk | disco | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, water, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | 7up | tea | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, mouse, goat
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the goat##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | horse | goat | mouse | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, carrot, zucchini, grapefruit
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating carrot and the person eating spinach##2
2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | grapefruit | carrot | zucchini | spinach |

