.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, car, skateboard, helicopter
1. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |
| Transport   | tram | skateboard | helicopter | car |

